Original:
滷味、水餃非常優秀，調酒也算中上的一間酒吧。

店內裝潢走既中式也西式霓虹的風格，整間店是佛燈的紅色為主視覺XD
個人很喜歡他們的滷味跟水餃。
滷味很入味，鹹度適中也很香，也會附上辣醬做搭配，非常下酒！
水餃皮薄餡多，肉的調味適當也很紮實，搭配醬油及辣醬非常美味。

調酒相較於食物並沒有特別驚豔，
茶酒種類多，但個人認為茶的味道並沒有跟基酒特別調和，或是茶的香氣並沒有特別突出。
但調酒本身仍然是「中上品質」的調酒，只是食物真的太優秀了XD

整體來說絕對是值得推薦的酒吧，比較適合想吃台式小點搭配調酒的人來！
EN:
Loi and dumplings are very good, and bartending is also considered a bar in the middle.

The interior decoration of the store is both Chinese and Western neon style. The entire store is the red of the Buddha lamp as the main visual XD
Personally I like their four and dumplings.
Lochi is very delicious, and the saltiness is moderate and fragrant. It will also be accompanied by hot sauce for matching, which is very wine!
The dumplings are thin and have a lot of skin, and the flavoring of the meat is proper and solid. It is very delicious with soy sauce and hot sauce.

The bartender is not particularly amazing than food,
There are many types of tea wine, but I personally think that the taste of tea is not specially reconciled with the base wine, or the aroma of tea is not particularly prominent.
But the bartending itself is still the bartender of "middle quality", but the food is really excellent XD

On the whole, it is definitely a recommended bar. It is more suitable for people who want to eat tabletop small dots with bartender!

Original:
店裡的氛圍整體營造有一種說不出來的感受
或許是我平時本身到酒吧會有一些壓力，但這家店卻沒有想像中的那種壓力。

也許是剛好當天Bartender談吐比較自然風趣，自然而然就沒有什麼壓力。

因為與朋友只有兩人，於是就選擇了吧台的位置，點酒的時候Bartender問了我們平時喝酒的習慣，平時喝紅白酒的我對於調酒真的不是很了解，於是請Bartender介紹，當時服務的Bartender我雖然不記得名子但我記得他的光頭特徵，很風趣的跟我說調酒很看個人口味，不過我的口味適合全部的人。
我聽內心噗次的笑了，我倒是要試試看適不適合我隨後他只問我要甜還是不甜，對於飲品沒甜就不行的我果斷的選擇前者。

過了幾分鐘後，上了一杯外表很華麗的酒。
他說他今天心情好才有這麼多裝飾，要不然就是會像隔壁的酒那樣平淡，我轉眼一看忍不住笑了出來，也差異太大了吧。

第一口喝下有著濃厚的水果香氣，又有點熟悉卻又說不出的花香，尾韻帶有一點苦甘，不知道是不是我是個調酒初心者還是他真的很厲害，這杯酒真的著實的打到我的心。
發自內心的稱讚之後，感覺的出來Bartender也非常開心，因為他整整請我喝了四次Shot，我都懷疑他們有沒有賺我的錢了，不過這印證了做人嘴巴要甜這件事，雖然我是發自內心啦！

當天喝的比較晚一點，大概兩點左右發現店裡越來越熱絡，來的客人似乎都與Bartender很熟識，一問之下才發現原來這邊到這個時間其他間酒吧收店後會來這邊放鬆聊天。
這讓我感覺有一點像日劇深夜食堂，下了班來到店裡聊聊今天發生的事，就我一個旁人看來莫名的有一種溫馨的感覺。
EN:
The atmosphere in the store has a sense of unspeakable feeling as a whole
Perhaps I usually have some pressure in the bar, but this shop does not have the kind of pressure in imagination.

Perhaps it was just that Bartender's talk was more natural and funny that day, and naturally there was no pressure.

Because there are only two people with friends, I chose the position of the bar. When I ordered the wine, Bartender asked us about the habit of drinking. I usually do n’t know much about bartender. So I asked Bartender to introduce. At that time, the service was at the time. Although Bartender I don't remember the name, I remember his bald characteristics. I told me that bartender is very personal, but my taste is suitable for all people.
I laughed in my heart, but I had to try it if it was suitable for me. Then he only asked me if I wanted me to be sweet or not sweet. I decisively chose the former for the drink.

After a few minutes, a glass of wine with gorgeous appearance was put in.
He said that he was in a good mood today to have so many decorations. Otherwise, he would be as bland as the wine next door. I couldn't help laughing at a glance, and the difference was too big.

The first drink has a strong fruits aroma, and a little familiar but indescribable floral fragrance. The tail rhyme has a bit bitterness. I don’t know if I am a bartender. Hit my heart really.
After praising from the heart, Bartender was very happy, because he asked me to drink SHOT four times, and I doubt whether they have made my money, but this confirms that it is sweet to be a human mouth. Although I am from the heart!

I drank a little later on the day. About two o'clock, I found that the store was getting hotter and warm. The guests who came seemed to be familiar with Bartender. I found that I would come here to close the shop here. Relax and chat here.
This makes me feel a bit like a late night cafeteria in the Japanese drama. When I came to work in the store to talk about what happened today, I seemed inexplicable with a warm feeling.

Entering the bar, the bartender will welcome you enthusiastically.Those who eat alone often sit on the bar of the bar.My drink, I chose Gui Gongzi. This should be their signboard (?) The drink is really fragrant, and the wine is good, so no, they do not skimming!The speech is really beautiful.
